languages.text: "Не стоит сравнивать наши миры, элантах. Я взращивала это место годами, лелеяла и ухаживала, как за цветущим садом. Твой же мир еще молод и неловок — и так и должно быть".
"We should not compare our worlds, elantach. Mine is a blossoming garden that I have tended and cherished for years. Yours is still young and ungraceful — as it should be."

languages.text: “没有必要比较彼此的世界，外界人。我的世界是经过我多年精心打理的花园，而你的世界还很年轻、很荒芜，那正是它该有的模样。”
languages.original_text: "We should not compare our worlds, elantach. Mine is a blossoming garden that I have tended and cherished for years. Yours is still young and ungraceful — as it should be."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «No deberíamos comparar nuestros mundos, elantach. El mío es un jardín floreciente que llevo años cultivando y manteniendo. El tuyo aún es joven y rudimentario; como debería ser».
languages.original_text: "We should not compare our worlds, elantach. Mine is a blossoming garden that I have tended and cherished for years. Yours is still young and ungraceful — as it should be."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Nos mondes ne sont pas comparables, elantach. Le mien est un jardin luxuriant que j'entretiens depuis de nombreuses années. Le vôtre est encore jeune et disgracieux, et c'est normal. »
languages.original_text: "We should not compare our worlds, elantach. Mine is a blossoming garden that I have tended and cherished for years. Yours is still young and ungraceful — as it should be."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Wir sollten unsere Welten nicht vergleichen, Elantach. Meine ist ein blühender Garten, den ich seit Jahren hege und pflege. Eure ist noch jung und ohne Anmut – wie sie sein sollte."
languages.original_text: "We should not compare our worlds, elantach. Mine is a blossoming garden that I have tended and cherished for years. Yours is still young and ungraceful — as it should be."

languages.text: 「エランタよ、我らの世界を比べてはいけない。我の世界は何年も手入れをし、大切にしてきた花園だ。お前の世界はまだ若く、未熟…当然の姿だ」
languages.original_text: "We should not compare our worlds, elantach. Mine is a blossoming garden that I have tended and cherished for years. Yours is still young and ungraceful — as it should be."

traits.locale_text: 「エランタよ、我らの世界を比べてはいけない。我の世界は何年も手入れをし、大切にしてきた花園だ。お前の世界はまだ若く、未熟…当然の姿だ」
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Dünyalarımızı karşılaştırmamalıyız elantach. Benim dünyam; yıllarca bakıp büyüttüğüm, filizlenen bir bahçe. Seninkiyse hâlâ genç ve acımasız, olması gerektiği gibi yani."
